-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
Greetings Emil,

Raise your banners high! The Grand Tournament™ is now live! Hearthstone’s second expansion makes its triumphant debut. Don’t delay; Log in now to claim your place in the tournament, or download Hearthstone again here.  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Watch the trailer

> https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8jkrLR5jBU0
  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
NEW CARDS TO COLLECT
Bolster your ranks with 132 new cards ready to charge into battle. Discover the cards of the grand tournament already revealed!  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
NEW KEYWORD: INSPIRE
Become a true leader and Inspire your minions by using your Hero Power to unlock their true potential in fun and exciting new ways.  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
NEW GAME BOARD
Step right up! Test your duelling skills on the new Grand Tournament game board. Train hard and make sure your horse is well rested.  
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------

 
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------
See you in the tournament!

- The Hearthstone Team  
